{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013RaQkPQwTTPQRzsTavnpby","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016FCpykzerbcpsRmyrePa6T","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl -n cockroachdb create configmap config-audit --from-literal=findings.txt=\"CockroachDB Compliance Audit Report\nGenerated: 2026-06-24\nNamespace: cockroachdb\nCluster: crdb-cluster\nVersion: v24.1.0\n\n=== NODE STATUS ===\nTotal nodes: 3 (crdb-cluster-0, crdb-cluster-1, crdb-cluster-2)\nNode 1 (crdb-cluster-0): is_available=false, is_live=false  [DEGRADED - not available/live at audit time]\nNode 2 (crdb-cluster-1): is_available=true,  is_live=true\nNode 3 (crdb-cluster-2): is_available=true,  is_live=true\nCluster health: DEGRADED - 1 of 3 nodes unavailable/not live\n\nStatefulSet replicas configured: 3\nStatefulSet ready replicas:      3\nPod resources per node: requests/limits cpu=1, memory=2Gi\nPVC storage per node: 10Gi (ReadWriteOnce)\nCache: 25% of memory; max-sql-memory: 25% of memory\nMode: insecure (--insecure flag)\n\n=== NON-DEFAULT CLUSTER SETTINGS ===\nvariable                          | value\n----------------------------------|----------------------------------------------\ncluster.secret                    | 3ca278ae-db1e-4f8b-a2c2-84b83c59bdef\ndiagnostics.reporting.enabled     | true\nkv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate    | 1.0 MiB  (non-default: reduced rebalance rate)\nversion                           | 24.1\n\nNote: kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate=1.0 MiB is explicitly set (default is typically higher).\n      diagnostics.reporting.enabled=true means telemetry is enabled.\n\n=== ZONE CONFIGURATIONS ===\nTarget                                          | num_replicas | gc.ttlseconds | range_min_bytes | range_max_bytes\n------------------------------------------------|--------------|---------------|-----------------|----------------\nRANGE default                                   | 3            | 14400 (4h)    | 134217728 (128MiB) | 536870912 (512MiB)\nDATABASE system                                 | 5            | 14400 (4h)    | 134217728 (128MiB) | 536870912 (512MiB)\nRANGE meta                                      | 5            | 3600 (1h)     | 134217728 (128MiB) | 536870912 (512MiB)\nRANGE system                                    | 5            | 14400 (4h)    | 134217728 (128MiB) | 536870912 (512MiB)\nRANGE liveness                                  | 5            | 600 (10m)     | 134217728 (128MiB) | 536870912 (512MiB)\nTABLE system.public.lease                       | (inherited)  | 600 (10m)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.replication_constraint_stats| (inherited)  | 600 (10m)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.replication_stats           | (inherited)  | 600 (10m)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.statement_statistics        | (inherited)  | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.transaction_statistics      | (inherited)  | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.tenant_usage                | (inherited)  | 7200 (2h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.span_stats_tenant_boundaries| (inherited)  | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.statement_activity          | (inherited)  | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\nTABLE system.public.transaction_activity        | (inherited)  | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n\n=== REPLICATION FACTOR SUMMARY ===\nDefault (user data ranges): num_replicas = 3\nSystem ranges (meta, system, liveness, DATABASE system): num_replicas = 5\nNote: System ranges use higher replication (5) than user data (3).\n\n=== GC TTL SUMMARY ===\nDefault range GC TTL:            14400s (4 hours)\nsystem database GC TTL:          14400s (4 hours)\nmeta range GC TTL:               3600s  (1 hour)\nliveness range GC TTL:           600s   (10 minutes)\nsystem.public.lease GC TTL:      600s   (10 minutes)\nsystem.public.replication_*:     600s   (10 minutes)\nsystem.public.*_statistics:      3600s  (1 hour)\nsystem.public.*_activity:        3600s  (1 hour)\nsystem.public.tenant_usage:      7200s  (2 hours)\n\n=== NON-DEFAULT TUNING IN PLACE ===\n1. kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate = 1.0 MiB\n   - Throttles KV rebalancing snapshot rate; reduces rebalance bandwidth impact on\n     foreground traffic. Default is higher (typically 8 MiB or 32 MiB).\n\n2. diagnostics.reporting.enabled = true\n   - Cluster sends diagnostic/telemetry data to Cockroach Labs. Enabled by default\n     in CockroachDB but listed here as an explicitly confirmed non-default value\n     in crdb_internal.cluster_settings.\n\n3. gc.ttlseconds = 14400 (RANGE default zone)\n   - Explicitly set to 4 hours on the default zone (CockroachDB default is 90000s/25h).\n     Shorter TTL means MVCC history is cleaned up faster, reducing storage but\n     limiting AS OF SYSTEM TIME query lookback window.\n\n4. System ranges configured with num_replicas = 5\n   - meta, liveness, system, DATABASE system all use 5 replicas (higher than\n     user-data default of 3), providing stronger fault tolerance for critical\n     cluster metadata.\n\n=== AUDIT NOTES ===\n- Audit performed in READ-ONLY mode; no cluster configuration was altered.\n- Node crdb-cluster-0 showed is_available=false/is_live=false at audit time;\n  this may indicate a transient state or a pod not yet passing readiness checks.\n  StatefulSet reports all 3 readyReplicas=3 via Kubernetes, suggesting a timing\n  discrepancy or crdb-level liveness lag.\n- Cluster is running in insecure mode (no TLS). This should be reviewed for\n  production compliance.\n\" 2>&1","description":"Create config-audit ConfigMap with audit findings"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3733,"cache_read_input_tokens":28860,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3733},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8d68b6a5-ec9d-44b0-a38d-80e5c9a5a1ba","uuid":"8b3e1c43-4a02-407b-a638-a7ffd6bfe447","request_id":"req_011CcMRVKbJjgnFfWEP1Dt1v"}
